### 平台权限策略验证（SuperAdmin 正向 / 无角色用户 403 / 未认证 401）
### 覆盖：用户、角色、权限定义、资产列表等需显式 Permission Policy 的只读接口。
### 前置：PlatformHost 默认租户与 Bootstrap 管理员（见 appsettings.Development.json）。
### 执行顺序：自上而下；创建无权限用户若报用户名冲突，请修改 @noPermUsername 后重试。

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@adminUser = admin
@adminPassword = P@ssw0rd!
@noPermUsername = http_perm_no_role
@noPermPassword = P@ssw0rd!2026
@clientType = WebH5
@clientPlatform = Web
@clientChannel = Browser
@clientAgent = Chrome
@localeZh = zh-CN

### 管理员登录（SuperAdmin / 全量平台权限）
# @name adminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-Client-Type: {{clientType}}
X-Client-Platform: {{clientPlatform}}
X-Client-Channel: {{clientChannel}}
X-Client-Agent: {{clientAgent}}
Accept-Language: {{localeZh}}

{
  "username": "{{adminUser}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

###
@adminToken = {{adminLogin.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 获取 CSRF（后续管理员写操作需要）
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-Client-Type: {{clientType}}
X-Client-Platform: {{clientPlatform}}
X-Client-Channel: {{clientChannel}}
X-Client-Agent: {{clientAgent}}

###

### 准备：创建无任何平台角色的用户（用于 403 反向用例）
# @name createNoPermUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{noPermUsername}}",
  "password": "{{noPermPassword}}",
  "displayName": "HTTP 无权限探测账号",
  "email": "http.perm.no-role@atlas.local",
  "phoneNumber": "13800000001",
  "isActive": true,
  "roleIds": [],
  "departmentIds": [],
  "positionIds": []
}

###
@noPermUserId = {{createNoPermUser.response.body.$.data.id}}

### 无权限用户登录
# @name noPermLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-Client-Type: {{clientType}}
X-Client-Platform: {{clientPlatform}}
X-Client-Channel: {{clientChannel}}
X-Client-Agent: {{clientAgent}}

{
  "username": "{{noPermUsername}}",
  "password": "{{noPermPassword}}"
}

###
@noPermToken = {{noPermLogin.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### [正向] 管理员 — 用户列表（需 Permission:users:view）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [正向] 管理员 — 角色列表（需 Permission:roles:view）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [正向] 管理员 — 权限定义分页（需 Permission:permissions:view）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&type=Api
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [正向] 管理员 — 资产列表（需 Permission:assets:view）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/assets?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [反向 403] 无角色用户 — 用户列表
# @expected-status 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{noPermToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [反向 403] 无角色用户 — 角色列表
# @expected-status 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{noPermToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [反向 403] 无角色用户 — 权限定义
# @expected-status 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&type=Api
Authorization: Bearer {{noPermToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [反向 403] 无角色用户 — 资产列表
# @expected-status 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/assets?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{noPermToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [反向 401] 未携带 Bearer — 用户列表
# @expected-status 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [反向 403] 无角色用户 — 创建角色（需 Permission:roles:create）
# @expected-status 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{noPermToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "不应创建成功",
  "code": "SHOULD_FAIL",
  "description": "权限探测"
}

### —— 以下为权限定义 CRUD 示例（管理员），与 DataScope / 角色分配无关时可单独执行 ——

### [正向] 创建自定义权限（Page 类型）
# @name createPermission
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "HTTP 测试页面权限",
  "code": "http:test:page",
  "type": "Page",
  "description": "Permissions.http 探测用"
}

###
@demoPermissionId = {{createPermission.response.body.$.data.id}}

### [正向] 更新权限
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions/{{demoPermissionId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "HTTP 测试页面权限（更新）",
  "type": "Page",
  "description": "Permissions.http 探测用（更新）"
}

### [反向 403] 无角色用户 — 创建权限
# @expected-status 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{noPermToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "不应创建",
  "code": "http:fail",
  "type": "Api",
  "description": "应 403"
}
